code: import{FETCH_PHOTO,TOGGLE_PHOTO}from'./types';export var fetchPhoto=function fetchPhoto(){return function(dispatch){var UNSPLASH_API_KEY="".concat(process.env.REACT_APP_UNSPLASH_API_KEY);var random_page_num=Math.floor(Math.random()*62);fetch("https://api.unsplash.com/collections/19428159/photos/?page= "+random_page_num+"&per_page=1&client_id="+UNSPLASH_API_KEY).then(function(res){return res.json();}).then(function(result){var photo=result[0];dispatch({type:FETCH_PHOTO,payload:photo});}).catch(function(error){console.log(error);});};};export var togglePhoto=function togglePhoto(event){return function(dispatch){dispatch({type:TOGGLE_PHOTO,payload:event});};};
